          body: "Small, elite squads of senior engineers. No juniors, no bloat, just pure technical momentum."
        },
        {
          label: "04. Complex Specialization",
          body: "We thrive in the \"too hard\" category. Finance, healthcare, and enterprise-grade products are our playground."
        }
      ]
    },
